item.title: What's going on in search with Jamie Marsden
item.description: Dan talks to SEO veteran Jamie Marsdon about recent Google changes, Panda and Penguin and how companies can respond. There are some great insights here for small and large companies about SEO in general, outsourcing, link building tactics and how to best avoid ending up in the bad books with Google.
